msg: Earlier, exception/signal handler returned control to interrupted code during JIT breakpoint processing, so it
restored all unmodified processor registers including processor flags.
Now control is returned to interrupted code directly from breakpoint handler using si_transfer_control function. This
function restores general processor registers, but it does not restore processor flags modified during breakpoint
